text:
Dr Chew is very experienced and detailed.
With her background in Internal Medicine, she diagnosed my wife's Auto Immune condition. My whole family sees her for stomach issues and treatment is very effective.

Clinic is usually full of patients.
LC and Rebecca work relentless round the clock. Expect long waiting time.

Just contacted the clinic. Wanting to bring my 78 year old mum for consultation. The lady who attended to the call asks me a question and before I can answer, she interrupts me, and assumes a position. The customer service is equally important as consulting the doctor. Thus, I would highly recommend not to consult with this clinic.
Dr Chew's consultations are extremely detailed and thorough, which explains the wait time.
Very rude on the phone. Unable to give a proper time and wants client to wait for hours. No thanks.
Waited 3hrs to see a doc. Wont bother coming again
